{"tid":1531562,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"愛上了工人姐姐","createTime":"2019-09-02T09:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T09:57:54.000Z","uid":196627,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"195543e939807eae360d27d0a3b68689193d4149","tid":1531562,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:10:12.000Z","msg":"小咁的<br />\n小弟廿幾歲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n家中不嬲有請菲傭<br />\n由細帶大我<br />\n佢四十幾歲<br />\n小肥<br />\n少少似胡孟青<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢月尾要番屋企了<br />\n我知道之後日日都無精神無心機賭波馬同返工<br />\n發夢又見到佢<br />\n應唔應該表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留住佢？<br />\n<br />\n琴晚屋企無人<br />\n兩個人獨處<br />\n開套韓劇 (假如愛有天意) 叫佢一齊睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點知出事了<br />\n<br />\n兩個人睇愛情劇<br />\n較暗個燈<br />\n本應浪漫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但工人姐姐不太投入<br />\n成日睇手機<br />\n我睇到兩個主角湖邊相倚之時<br />\n襯勢攬住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢無反抗無反應無出聲無表情<br />\n紙紮公仔一樣<br />\n勉勉強強睇完套戲就各自訓<br />\n我眼光光到天光<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n買左幾場波<br />\n仲輸尻埋<br />\n點知<br />\n第二日先知大鑊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呀呀呀<br />\n我Fungaying唔係人<br />\n做左件錯事<br />\n好後悔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又爛賭又咸濕<br />\n賭波馬又輸多贏少<br />\n欠人債唔還<br />\n仲想溝工人姐姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第二日<br />\n工人姐姐同我老母講我搓揉佢個乳房<br />\n天呀<br />\n我有西揸佢波咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屈尻我<br />\n我手指邊掂過下佢個廿蚊雞難鬼街邊胸圍炸<br />\n好彩老母吊兩句就算<br />\n工人姐姐已無希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我Fungaying決定叫雞算<br />\n同買多幾手5號仔懷念佢"},{"pid":"00f9cdddf6c693efe8d9d09331b136d30f1ab27d","tid":1531562,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:10:58.000Z","msg":"利申:非假膠非gay<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89d991d3275e76b05dc8cb76961e7431010b7cf2","tid":1531562,"uid":312923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30f5f5a8f7015cf882e3376a228d0200e89e6567","tid":1531562,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"89d991d3275e76b05dc8cb76961e7431010b7cf2","tid":1531562,"uid":312923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:12:56.000Z","msg":"搞唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8f0f6a94f47215de1959e5993b612d279bc96e4","tid":1531562,"uid":26429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"HR 你唔係有閪既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5e43a58ef1a6ef87e239d7c13c8212bb95fa3f","tid":1531562,"uid":72564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"睇到左扯左"},{"pid":"32ad5608e172a3792299a49c8ce159054be2141c","tid":1531562,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8f0f6a94f47215de1959e5993b612d279bc96e4","tid":1531562,"uid":26429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:21:48.000Z","msg":"HR 你唔係有閪既咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:26:11.000Z","msg":"我會繼續以謙卑態度聆聽各位意見"},{"pid":"5680064ed3c8c9fc1d826e8bfc7c4cbadaf53063","tid":1531562,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b5e43a58ef1a6ef87e239d7c13c8212bb95fa3f","tid":1531562,"uid":72564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:24:20.000Z","msg":"睇到左扯左"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:26:31.000Z","msg":"G持"},{"pid":"bdc592979fdc54e11968989db111a4e0eb76cddf","tid":1531562,"uid":219337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:30:56.000Z","msg":"你細個果時工人姐姐無幫你破處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"058c4a654ca3e73d9472f32ad23c3931ccc1cb16","tid":1531562,"uid":123848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T09:57:54.000Z","msg":"居然無屌到，重作<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}